{"tid":1663262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]職業轉生：　旗手/畫家","createTime":"2019-10-19T10:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T14:38:29.000Z","uid":136686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3071d0b08f70f69ae516fae695362a087102a716","tid":1663262,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，而家出面無曬旗手，可能因為支旗越來越難整<br />\n咁如果我套裝比個旗手玩會點樣<br />\n示意圖 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWsQHi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWsQHi5.jpg&h=ee52f991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKuWCUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKuWCUY.jpg&h=6f955695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塊板係Ａ２尺寸，係美術用品鋪買到<br />\n（旺角，油麻地或灣仔）<br />\n要再買一堆Ａ２尺寸嘅新聞紙（或者宜家家私嘅捲裝畫紙）<br />\n仲有用四個夾夾實堆紙<br />\n<br />\n木板＋畫紙點都易準備過塑膠旗<br />\n如果跟番以前旗手嘅玩法，可能需要事先準備顏料油滿張紙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MyTPXU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMyTPXU0.jpg&h=ce9468b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n字數上限係４個<br />\n係一個籃球埸嘅距離都清晰可見<br />\n<br />\n如果你想COSPLAY戰地畫家<br />\n你可能需要一個畫筒用黎裝畫，或者其他你想裝嘅野<br />\n同樣可以係美術用品鋪買到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/19/180044_43f3c6cd783b22ea6d1f7809f68c55c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F19%2F180044_43f3c6cd783b22ea6d1f7809f68c55c4.jpg&h=ff1aa397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過木板同同畫筒對於Black Block黎講好顯眼 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果不幸遇到福建暴徒，塊木板仲可以嚇下佢地<br />\n係自衛反擊嘅情況甚至可以請佢食板框同板角<br />\n<br />\n至於點樣同持盾暴徒作戰就唔係我嘅研究範圍<br />\n我亦唔建議同綠衫正面衝突（戴頭盔）"},{"pid":"ea5125355838f5f8703e2abb015f5a36796d9752","tid":1663262,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"陳帆：港鐵如不再受破壞一、兩周內可回復正常服務<br />\n咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要攬炒"},{"pid":"531d3ef6da69c987e537c2fee2bc3911e4915960","tid":1663262,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8792805edcb838df72b7b5bb386910d07520bcd4","tid":1663262,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}